## Commit Message Format

Use conventional commits:

```
[type]([scope]): Brief description

Types:
- feat:     New feature or prompt
- fix:      Bug fix or correction
- docs:     Documentation update
- refactor: Code restructure (no behavior change)
- sync:     Cross-platform sync update
- chore:    Maintenance tasks

Scope (optional):
- editorial, social, email, ads, media, core, shared, integrations
```

### Examples:
```
feat(editorial): Add finance vertical prompt template
fix(shared): Correct source registry URLs
docs: Update README with v5.1 features
sync: Update Notion/Linear with latest GitHub changes
chore: Add .cursorrules and SYNC_STATUS.md
```

